OL,5, A teenager was seen pushing a boy into 
OL,6, a river shortly before he drowned, an  
OL,7, inquest has heard.                     
OL,9,FChristopher Kapessa, 13, died after the
OL,10,Fincident in the River Cynon in         
OL,11,FFernhill, Rhondda Cynon Taf, in 2019.  
OL,13,FThe inquest heard another boy, then 14,
OL,14,Fwho cannot be named for legal reasons, 
OL,15,Fpushed Christopher into the water.     
OL,17,FChristopher, who could not swim,       
OL,18,Fimmediately got into difficulty and    
OL,19,Fother children jumped in to help but he
OL,20,Fcould not be saved.                    
